title: I spent all my youtube money on T-SHIRTS for my viewers.
description:
We fly to Los Angeles on April 22nd, so supporters in the USA, especially, should HMU immediately (with address and other details).  The t-shirts are free —we ask that you pay only for the cost of the postage stamp (meaning: it'll come in a really cheap envelope).  ;-)   Links:
(1) https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel
(2) The storybook project (translated into several languages), as mentioned: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZEkgohG7k7pperokk75ic6XpyLqy7MUw

(4) Against reducetarianism ("being pragmatic is not selling out your fundamental principles"): Brass Tacks: Reducetarian Pragmatism vs. Vegan Optimism. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WSJSfGGGsUo
